data.description: Adorable home with daylight basement nestled in the cute city of Drain and nice community. The main living area of this home is upstairs with great views of the valley and mountains. The home has hardwood floors and carpet.. A unique downstairs playroom/family room with newer laminate floors and access to garage and porch with hot tub. Property is private with many different amenities. A newly installed well in 2022, covered RV parking, an electric gate, a fully fenced yard, along with outbuildings and lots of parking. Lots of area for Gardeners including raise beds, flowers, and fruit trees. Come take a look and fall in love with the yard and privacy. Come and see what this beautiful home has to offer.
